<p>Hi,</p>

<p>We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to choose a new one:</p>

<p style="margin: 24px 0;">
  <a href="<%= edit_password_url(@user.password_reset_token) %>" class="btn">Reset your password</a>
</p>

<p class="muted">This link will expire in 15 minutes.</p>

<p class="muted">If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
